lead_paragraph: Lamar Jackson lost the ball, No. 11 Louisville lost the game to rival Kentucky and it remains to be seen how it all will impact the Heisman Trophy race that once belonged to the Cardinals quarterback just a few weeks ago.

headline.print_headline: Kentucky Beats No. 11 Louisville 41-38 After Jackson Fumble
